      <title>波兰财政部长敦促检察官对奥伦进行审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/polish-finance-minister-urges-prosecutors-to-scrutinize-orlen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰财政部长安杰伊·多曼斯基 (Andrzej Domanski) 周五表示，在国营 Orlen SA 能源集团支付 4 亿美元购买其从未收到的石油的消息曝光后，波兰国家检察官应该“彻底”调查该能源集团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/polish-finance-minister-urges-prosecutors-to-scrutinize-orlen</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在选举年推动取消 70 亿美元学生债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/student-loan-forgiveness-biden-cancels-7-billion-more-in-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统将免除 74 亿美元的联邦学生债务，这是他为借款人提供救济的最新举措，并在寻求连任时兑现了降低高等教育成本的竞选承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/student-loan-forgiveness-biden-cancels-7-billion-more-in-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美海军新战舰遭遇员工流失困扰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/warship-maker-can-t-keep-enough-skilled-workers-to-build-navy-s-new-vessel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据该项目的一份服务文件，生产美国海军新型护卫舰的造船厂因未能“达到中型舰艇的工程和熟练劳动力水平”而陷入困境，该项目目前预计将推迟三年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/warship-maker-can-t-keep-enough-skilled-workers-to-build-navy-s-new-vessel</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称王毅在布林肯通话中谴责伊朗大使馆袭击事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/china-says-wang-yi-condemned-iran-embassy-attack-in-blinken-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，其最高外交官在与国务卿安东尼·布林肯的通话中讨论了中东的紧张局势，突显了人们对持续六个月的加沙冲突可能升级的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/china-says-wang-yi-condemned-iran-embassy-attack-in-blinken-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:36:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登誓言支持日本和菲律宾，因为中国震动了盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/biden-vows-to-back-japan-philippines-as-china-rattles-allies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登表示，他致力于“深化与日本和菲律宾的海上和安全关系”，因为他试图向担心中国在争议水域日益强硬行动的盟友保证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/biden-vows-to-back-japan-philippines-as-china-rattles-allies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 21:06:05 GMT</pubDate>
